txt.en: These materials look perfect for wall repairs ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

'If only half my friends would put in the effort you have just done for me. Thank you, you seem to have an excellent understanding of carpentry. I could not have picked better materials myself -- as if I would have had time! I am most grateful. Now I just need to find out where to put everything... no, do not mind me. I will ask for your help again should I require.'
TBD Frustrated Carpenter can be found at TBD.\n\nYou have collected a reasonable amount of supplies TBD Frustrated Carpenter can use to repair the walls of Jirush. Return to him with your findings.
These materials look perfect for wall repairs ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
TBD, a carpenter, is frustrated by the repairs to Jirush's battlements and the lack of a proper crew to help him out. Collect supplies from around the city for him.

'I am all for freedom fighting, but this is simply unbearable.... What? No, what do you care for Jirush's troubles? These battlements are falling apart, and no one will do anything about it! Half of my carpentry crew has left to join the rebels in the hills, leaving me with a mountain of tasks. I do not even have time to collect the supplies I need!\n\n'If you have enough time to listen to an old carpenter's ravings, perhaps you could track down some good materials for me.'
Materials to repair the walls can be found scattered throughout TBD.\n\nTBD has asked for your help playing courier and collecting supplies from around the city.
